        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 3. Herdmania mentula sp. nov. (A, E, WAM Z11756; B-D, WAM Z11771;F, WAM Z11761): A, body from left side showing muscles. B, dorsal tubercule; C, portion of dorsal lamina; D, gut and gonad; E, F, distal part of gut and gonads, showing gonoducal openings and membranes, and anal border. Scale bars: A, D = 5.0mm; B, C, E, F = 1.0mm." ;
